betterquesting:10.desc:8:
As I faced my opponents after my Ascension, I increasingly became more and more aware of a new power, one probing me, testing me.
Is it fate? Is it the Fractallite behind it? Or is it someone or something else completely.
That much I cannot yet say, but what I can say is that, if I want to keep following the steps of the Arbiter, I must face yet another trial.
One that will test my worthiness.
